                },
                "message": "Fix cache extraction for multiple files (#7561)\n\nCloses: https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/7559\n\nAs shared on the issue when having a multi file output on the cache in\nthe form of a zip file the extraction extracts into an incorrect folder\nstructure having the name of the file as part of the path:\n```\n├── lib_api.h\n│   └── lib_api.h\n├── lib.cpp\n│   └── lib.cpp\n├── lib.h\n│   └── lib.h\n```\nor `/tmp/tmp7015iv4v/build/lib_api.h/lib_api.h`\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: mv-python <matusvalo@users.noreply.github.com>",
